original_title: Playboy Video Centerfold: Victoria Silvstedt - Playmate of the Year 1997
overview: A Playboy produced documentary style video based on the modelling career of former Miss Sweeden, Victoria Silvstedt. Victoria went on to become Payboy's December 1996 playmate of the month and 1997 Playmate of the year. She stars as herself in the video.
title: Playboy Video Centerfold: Victoria Silvstedt - Playmate of the Year 1997
